snippet.title: Amber Heard Says It Was 'Incredibly Painful' To Re-Live Marriage To Johnny Depp
snippet.description:
As Johnny Depp's UK libel case against a British tabloid wraps up, Amber Heard addresses the media calling the trial "incredibly painful" to have to publicly re-live the intimate details of the break-up of her marriage to the actor.

#AmberHeard #JohnnyDepp
